[0m08:37:50.847493 [debug] [Thread-1 (]: Began executing node model.medallion_reference.fct_customer_health_score
[0m08:37:50.849032 [debug] [Thread-1 (]: Writing runtime sql for node "model.medallion_reference.fct_customer_health_score"
